{"tid":623880,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"聽力測試","createTime":"2018-04-10T10:40:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T15:03:53.000Z","uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"27d4c6daa87d35140e9742befba615d8b7e9c5d9","tid":623880,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:40:59.000Z","msg":"想做聽力測試，巴絲打有去過？<br />\n去醫院（仁安/浸會/...）好，定去d XX聽力中心好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：<br />\n本身兩隻耳都會間唔中會突然weeee聲+耳塞，維持十秒，之後又冇野。但感覺係每次weeeee完，聽覺會差左，近幾年連耳嗚聲都細聲左。曾經做過聽力測試，係密室聽唔同頻率既聲，果次就話我聽力正常。但我始終覺得我聽覺係有問題，所以想再搵個好地方再測試清楚。"},{"pid":"46c4f22b4d82255575468ece4ef7c32db63ca6ff","tid":623880,"uid":164060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T11:11:15.000Z","msg":"我睇完耳鼻喉科 再去聽力中心做 好快搞掂"},{"pid":"1c9d3a31d4386ffe9b2259a60ad1d138d99b01be","tid":623880,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T16:43:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我睇完耳鼻喉科 再去聽力中心做 好快搞掂</blockquote><br />\n邊間？可否開名比我參考下"},{"pid":"640a3f51f44e5cb58f3ace58df45b9dc1c141480","tid":623880,"uid":164060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c9d3a31d4386ffe9b2259a60ad1d138d99b01be","tid":623880,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T16:43:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我睇完耳鼻喉科 再去聽力中心做 好快搞掂</blockquote><br />\n邊間？可否開名比我參考下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T15:03:53.000Z","msg":"香港聽力 係尖沙咀亞太中心"}]}